{"tid":940311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭小巴排隊打尖嘅人好PK!","createTime":"2018-12-14T00:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T03:17:52.000Z","uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a8bb2f4437d67b809228e9bad22e6da974f7f832","tid":940311,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"本來以為上倒車，但遇到前面有人用呢兩種打尖法就玩完。<br />\n<br />\n1，前面有人Freind搭freind，即一個排緊，上車果陣就有第二條友突然去前面，同佢識果條友疊膊頭打尖。<br />\n<br />\n2，又係趁有車d人上緊果陣，突然打尖，呢種直頭硬插，但前面被插條友唔出聲，你後幾個身位，見到但d人上緊車，唔駛兩秒就上晒客，你又上啱啱上唔倒車。<br />\n<br />\n連續兩朝遇到呢種情況,PK!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5707f682c3cec07f84a9d0c4ea135dec09229181","tid":940311,"uid":172507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"打尖本身已經pk啦屌！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"0f89c5d0cb8e039f7613cee95e830b587cc7ebf9","tid":940311,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r